@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kgieit(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.18)))
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = (v1 / ((v0 + 0.17 * v1 + 0.22) - v0))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.70) * wp.abs(v2 + 0.41)) * v0)
    v2 = ((0.32 + v0) - 0.01)
    v2 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.43 * v0 + 0.91)) + ((v0 + 0.02 / v0 + 0.07) + (v2 + 0.25 * v1 + 0.25)))
    data[tid] = v0
